  documentation file names.
	
  02 Dev 2002; Matthew Kennedy <mkennedy@gentoo.org> ChangeLog,
  emacs-cvs-21.3.50.ebuild :

  Moved out of ~x86 into x86 (only for x86) by popular request. Reduced
